name.en,sr: Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_AU,en_GB,e: Stellen Sie vorgefertigte Antworten per ChatGPT bereit, wenn Sie mit Kunden in Ebay Nachrichten senden
short.en,sr: Provide canned responses by ChatGPT when you message with customers in Ebay

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT is a Chrome extension to help Ebay seller message with customers smoothly. It a free tool like Crisp magicRply or Drift GPT. Simply select the customer's question, then Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT will feedback the reply advice that given by GPT-3.5 Chatbot.

ğŸš€ Feature
â— Provide canned responses or reply template by ChatGPT base on the question of customers.
â— Simply select the question content.
â— Edit feedback from OpenAI in Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT to reply nicely to customers
â— Copy content by one click. 
â— Multiple output languages.

ğŸš€ Who is Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT for
Ebay Customer Service Helper with GPT is made for Ebay seller, customer service staff or someone need reply customer's question to solve their problem.

ğŸš€ How to use it
â¡ï¸ Make sure you have a ChatGPT account
â¡ï¸ Simply select any online content by your mouse
â¡ï¸ Click on Cmd+M (Mac) or Ctrl+M (Windows) to open the extension window
â¡ï¸ Choose what languages you need, and click "Ask for template"
â¡ï¸ The canned responses will displayed in the extension window in a minute.
